--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Random language feature ideas

  - Add comma operator

    var a = f(), 2; // a == 2

  - Optional braces in if() and while()

    if a < b {
    }

    while true {
    }

  - Unconditional loop statement

    loop {
    }

  - Better switch statement:

    switch (expr) {
      case (expr) { }
      case (expr) { }
      else { }
    }

  - Add sequence / iterator / foreach

    foreach(var i in seq) {
    }

    var i = seq.iterate();
    while(i.next()) {
      var v = i.current;
    }

    for(var i = seq.iterate(); i.hasCurrent; i.next()) {
      var v = i.current;
    }

